ModHeader.Author: HelixTechGroup
ModHeader.Description:
This is a part of Project Regenesys, A Vanilla++ take on additional features and rebalances.
All additions will try to feel natural to the game and add to its replay.
This module is the core module.

This Mod does nothing on its own.
This mod includes all common functionality and forms for use in Project Regenesys including:
Core system quest that holds the dataslate name, terminal reference, common keywords, etc.
